    </mrow>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </inline-formula> are the simulated and observed multi-year average extreme precipitation; 
 <italic class="italic">B</italic> is greater than 0 and smaller than 1; the closer 
 <italic class="italic">B</italic> is to 0, the better the performance of the GCM.
